’Щ@02bebfbf380c10498999c7864aa446a981e918430fac25b2d20790ff48c89172ЩgTitle: title: polars rename
Path: Signature
Content:
``> polars rename {flags} (columns) (new names)``
’Щ@62612e71cd1942ab163bb6b0a4e66d25ef980f822f789990196c010709d9358fЩНTitle: title: polars rename
Path: Parameters
Content:
``columns``
: Column(s) to be renamed. A string or list of strings.
``new names``
: New names for the selected column(s). A string or list of strings.
